12:41.891 --> 12:44.026
-(BLADES WHIRRING)
-(DOG BARKING)

12:53.196 --> 12:54.465
RAYMOND: Hey, Pete.

12:55.231 --> 12:56.698
Pretty fucking desolate.

12:57.340 --> 12:58.610
No shit.

12:58.678 --> 13:00.137
Thought there'd be
more people, I guess.

13:00.206 --> 13:01.538
-(PETER CHUCKLING)
-GARY: Major,

13:01.607 --> 13:04.415
he doesn't allow spectators
until the final stretch.

13:04.484 --> 13:05.982
