13:34.380 --> 13:35.407
Best in the world.

13:36.547 --> 13:37.876
Are you from here?

13:37.945 --> 13:39.140
Yeah, I'm from downstate.

13:39.209 --> 13:41.013
Ooh, so you the one.

13:41.082 --> 13:42.381
-What do you mean?
-The one what?

13:42.449 --> 13:44.349
Mr. Garraty here is the walker
from the home state.

13:44.418 --> 13:47.023
MAN ON SPEAKER:
<i> Warning. Warning, number 38.</i>

13:50.923 --> 13:51.962
HANK: Smart.

13:52.496 --> 13:54.357
What's smart?

13:54.426 --> 13:55.765
