while he's still fresh.

13:55.834 --> 13:57.328
He gets an idea
of what our limit is.

13:57.396 --> 13:59.367
Yeah, it seems
pretty fucking dumb to me.

13:59.435 --> 14:00.695
Well,

14:00.764 --> 14:02.770
big boy's gonna have
no problem walking an hour

14:02.839 --> 14:04.139
