14:37.838 --> 14:39.141
(HANK SCOFFS)

14:40.279 --> 14:41.945
(HUFFING)

14:42.014 --> 14:43.877
MAN ON SPEAKERS:<i> Warning.</i>
<i> Warning, number five.</i>

14:43.946 --> 14:45.911
