PETER: What the fuck?

14:56.491 --> 14:59.390
MAN ON SPEAKER:<i> Warning,</i>
<i> number five. Second warning.</i>

14:59.459 --> 15:01.257
HANK: Fuck, he's still
fucking down there!

15:01.325 --> 15:02.463
PETER: What's he doing, man?

15:02.532 --> 15:04.892
Holy shit!

15:04.961 --> 15:06.634
-PETER: Go on, get up!
-RAYMOND: Get up, Barkovitch.

15:06.703 --> 15:08.104
HANK: Jesus Christ!

15:08.173 --> 15:09.565
That dumbfuck's actually gonna
get his fucking ticket.

15:09.633 --> 15:11.504
Hey, come on, get up, man.
Stop playing.

15:11.572 --> 15:15.111
MAN ON SPEAKER:<i> Warning,</i>
<i> number five. Third warning.</i>

15:15.180 --> 15:17.080
-Get the fuck up, Barkovitch!
-PETER: Come on, man.

15:24.148 --> 15:25.519
HANK: Dumbfuck.

15:25.587 --> 15:27.090
Idiot.

15:28.854 --> 15:30.027
Dumbass.

15:30.892 --> 15:32.128
Better not trip, fucko.

15:32.929 --> 15:34.465
(PANTING) Y'all don't even know.

15:34.534 --> 15:36.362
Just bought myself a rest.

15:36.431 --> 15:39.198
