and the prize,
it certainly doesn't matter.

16:57.616 --> 16:58.946
-(PETER SCOFFS)
-What?

16:59.015 --> 17:00.581
That's some bullshit, Garraty.

17:00.649 --> 17:02.083
Okay.

17:02.152 --> 17:05.087
All right, well,
look at it like this.

17:05.156 --> 17:07.352
